revisionDesc.change: 2010-12-09 Piotr Bański: Added @xml:lang attributes and profileDesc/langUsage.

2010-12-01 Piotr Bański: Database name changed from eng-scr to eng.srp. I assume this dictionary to be close in nature to the previous scr-eng (current srp-eng) in that the latter contained Serbian with Montenegrin dialectal additions (thanks to Dr. Jerzy Molas of the University of Warsaw for his remarks on scr-eng, which I assume to hold for eng-scr, because they have the same origin in Ergane). TODO: identify the Montenegrin additions and mark them with <usg> elements.
